{"id":5063,"content":"<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">文化大革命</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">是内乱骤起，风云动荡的年代。然而，就是在这样动荡的年代，有一位</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">19</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">岁的高中一年级学生，从</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1967</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">11</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月到</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1968</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">4</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月中句，仅用半年时间，竟写就两部长达</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">40</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">余万字的政论文稿，对当时</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">轰轰烈烈</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">的</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">文化大革命</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">作出了自己的否定判断；对尚未折戟沉沙的林彪，对炙手可热的江青一伙，敢于无情揭露和辛辣鞭挞；对刘少奇同志所蒙受的干古奇冤大鸣不平。文稿广泛地涉及到我国政治、经济、军事、文化艺术、意识形态各个领域，内容充实，行文流畅，尤其后写的一部，结构严谨，笔锋犀利，论证的逻辑思维更趋成熟，这是一般青年难于达到的。他就是</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">文革</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"&nbsp;</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">蒙难第一中学生</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">--</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">吴晓飞</SPAN></FONT><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">!<BR><BR></FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　他看出了围剿</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">三家村</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">的险恶用心</SPAN></FONT><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><BR><BR></SPAN><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1949</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年春，吴晓飞出生于一个革命干部家庭，他是新中国的同龄人，从小勤学好问、酷爱文学，呀呀学语的时候，父亲就开始教他唐诗宋词。他爱听父辈们讲革命先烈的故事，那一个个悲壮的故事无不激荡着他的心。耳濡目染下，他形成了爱憎分明的性格。小学时期，老师们便喜爱这位好学生，踏入中学，吴晓飞更成熟了，追求更高了，他开始认真阅读马列著作和毛主席的著作，在年轻的心灵中树立了为实现共产主义而奋斗的理想。</SPAN></FONT><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><BR></SPAN><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　吴晓飞初中曾就读于福州市第</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">5</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">中学，教过他的老师都不约而同称赞他是刚直、勤于思考的学生，他的才华是公认的。</SPAN></FONT><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><BR></SPAN><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1965</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年底，全国报刊上继批判吴晗的《海瑞罢官》后，又发起了对</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">三家村</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">和《燕山夜话》的批判。《三家村札记》实际是从</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1961</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年起，在由北京市委书记处书记邓拓主编的北京市委理论刊物《前线》杂志上开辟的杂文专栏，由吴晗</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">(</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">北京市副市长</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">)</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">、邓拓和廖沫沙</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">(</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">北京市委统战部长</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">)</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">以</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">吴南星</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">的笔名供稿，先后发表了杂文</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">50</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">余篇。《燕山夜话》是邓拓从</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1961</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">3</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月起应约为《北京晚报》定期写知识性杂文而以</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">马南邨</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">为笔名开设的专栏。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">批判</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">三家村</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">，矛头直指中共北京市委现在这一点己经十分清楚，而在当时要对此作出正确的判断却不是一件容易的事情。但吴晓飞却在心中亮起了红灯。他疑惑了，他找来《三家村札记》和《燕山夜话》的每篇杂文，认真积极地阅读，专栏中的文章知识性强，文笔生动，针贬时弊，批评过高指标、瞎指挥、浮夸风，为广大读者所喜爱，为什么忽然被批为</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">歪曲党的百花齐放，百家争鸣的方针，主张让资产阶级思想泛滥</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">、</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">全面美化封建社会制度</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">借封建古人之尸，还资产阶级之魂</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">宣扬剥削阶级没落的人生哲学</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">，更有甚者，被认为是</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">恶毒攻击总路线、攻击大跃进</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">贯穿着一条同《海瑞骂皇帝》、《海瑞罢官》一脉相承的反党、反人民反社会主义的黑线，诬蔑和攻击以毛泽东同志为首的党中央，攻击党的总路线，极力支持被</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">罢</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\"></FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">了</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\"></FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">官</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\"></FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">的右倾机会主义分子的翻案进攻，支持封建势力和资本主义势力的猖狂进攻。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">这是怎么了？他的心中充满了</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">？</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">。学生最信赖的<?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags\" /><st1:PersonName w:st=\"on\" ProductID=\"莫过于\">莫过于</st1:PersonName>老师，为了弄清围剿《燕山夜话》的险恶用心，他在一个晚上找到了班主<st1:PersonName w:st=\"on\" ProductID=\"任严\">任严</st1:PersonName>老师，<st1:PersonName w:st=\"on\" ProductID=\"向严\">向严</st1:PersonName>老师倾诉心中的疑惑：从自己如何喜欢邓拓、吴晗、廖沫沙的文章，到报上为什么忽然冒出了那么多的批判文章，并且摆出了自己的想法：</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">这是不是有人故意在制造事端，借此而弄乱局面，整垮北京市委？</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">吴晓飞就这样详细地分析着形势，讲出自己的想法，一谈就是整整三个小时。然而，一个普通的中学教师，又能给他多少答案呢？随着时间的推移，吴晓飞心中的疑团越来越多了。</SPAN></FONT><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><BR><BR><BR></SPAN><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">造反有理</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">理</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">何在？</SPAN></FONT><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><BR><BR></SPAN><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1966</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">8</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月，吴晓飞的父亲调任南昌铁路局局长，他随父母的工作调动，也转学到南昌市第一中学就读。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">就在此时，中共八届十一中全会召开，宣告</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">文化大革命</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">的全面展开。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">8</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">18</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">日，在天安门广场举行了</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">庆祝无产阶级文化大革命</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">的大会，毛泽东穿上军装检阅了百万红卫兵。在会上，林彪发表讲话，号召红卫兵</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">大破一切剥削阶级的旧思想、旧文化、旧风俗、旧习惯</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">要把反革命的修正主义分子、资产阶级右派分子、资产阶级反动权威，彻底打倒、打垮，使他们威风扫地，永世不得翻身</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">!\"\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">我们要扫除一切害人虫，搬掉一切绊脚石</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">，在</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">革命就是造反</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">、</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">造反有理</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">的语调支持下，在</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">八</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">·</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">一八春风</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">的沐浴下，红卫兵采取了形形色色的</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">革命造反</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">行动，他们发起</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">更名运动</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">，禁止某些衣着、发式，破坏一些被认为是封、资、修的东西，抄</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">牛鬼蛇神</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">的家，多少私人财物被损、被破坏；更有甚者，发展到了打人、杀人，据统计，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1966</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">8,--9</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月间，北京市就打死</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">100</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">多人。一时间，打、砸、抢、抄这类现象愈演愈烈，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">破四旧</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">成为中国历史上最大的文化大破坏活动。红卫兵</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">破四旧</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">运动像恶性瘟疫一样，迅速向全国蔓延。知识界遭受了强烈的打击，知识界的知名人士普遍受到红卫兵的冲击，大学、中学、小学教师受凌辱者数以万计。</SPAN></FONT><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><BR></SPAN><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　红卫兵运动狂潮中的小将们，似乎缺少了理智。他们将自己的野性面充分暴露着，而吴晓飞面对这种种怪现象却有着他自己的思考：</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">为什么焚烧书籍、砸毁古迹？这不是要毁掉历史吗？中国那悠久的历史，创造了无数的财富，毁在我们手上，我们何以对得起祖先？</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">中国是五千年文明古国，为什么现在学生却可以打骂教师、批斗老师？这不符合中华民族的传统</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">!\"\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">随便抄家、打人，这是不合法的，为什么如今却如此轻而易举？打死人也不用负责，这又是为什么？</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">为什么林彪把毛泽东思想推到了宗教迷信的路上？敬奉毛主席为</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\"></FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">伟大的导师、伟大的领袖、伟大的舵手、伟大的统帅</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\"></FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">，宣扬</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\"></FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">万寿无疆</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\"></FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">，这不是唯心主义吗？他这是真帮忙还是帮倒忙？</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">吴晓飞头脑里顿时冒出了许多的</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">为什么？</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">这一连串的问号，在他脑海里翻腾、逐渐升华到忧党忧国的高度。他说道：</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">造反有理，究竟理何在？我解开这些错杂盘结的</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\"></FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">为什么</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\"></FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">的决心下定了，我深信通过真正的马列主义、毛泽东思想的精髓来解剖这些怪现象，一定能找到它的源头。如果不找出今天的症结，就难以确定明天怎么办</SPAN></FONT><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">!\"<BR></FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　就在吴晓飞苦苦思索着这些</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">为什么</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">的时候，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1966</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">9</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">5</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">日，中共中央、国务院发出《关于组织外地高等学校革命学生、中专学校革命学生代表和革命教职工代丧表来北京参观文化大革命的通知》，从</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">9</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size","title":"吴晓飞：\"文革\"蒙难第一中学生","time":1240164268999}